high_descs: Turn right and stand in front of the sink.
Pick the knife up on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn around and go stand in front of the stove.
Put the knife in the pot on the left side of the stove.
Pick the pot on the left side up from the stove.
Turn around and face the table in front of the coffee maker.
Put the pot down in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a put with a knife down on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, go straight to the fridge, turn right, go straight to the counter to the left of the sink.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, go straight and to the right to the oven.
Put the knife in the pot on the stove top closer to the front and on the left.
Take the pot from the stove top.
Turn around, go straight, turn left at the white table.
Put the pot on the right of the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and find the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the knife in front of the toaster.
Take the knife and go to the right around the kitchen to find the stove.
Place the knife in the front pan on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the knife it in.
Take the knife and pan and turn around to the coffee machine.
Place the pan and knife on the table in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife inside a pan and move both objects to a table.

high_descs: Turn around to your right and walk passed the refrigerator to the counter directly ahead.
Pick up the yellow-handled knife from the counter.
Walk back to the kitchen with the knife in front of the stove.
Place the knife in the bowl on the stove.
Pick up the bowl with the knife in it.
Walk the bowl and knife over to the white table with the tomato on it.
Set the bowl and knife on the table next to the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with the knife on the table with the tomato.
